OL,3,CMan who was left in coma from Covid is
OL,4,Creunited with doctors who saved his
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FOne of the first Covid-19 patients to
OL,8,Fbe treated in Surrey has been reunited
OL,9,Fwith the frontline staff who saved his
OL,10,Flife.
OL,12,FAnwar Chaudhri was admitted to the
OL,13,Fintensive care unit at Frimley Park
OL,14,FHospital in Camberley in 2020.
OL,16,FIn an emotional reunion he said he
OL,17,Fwould not be here today without the
OL,18,Fwork of the doctor and nurses there.
