OL,3,CMan who was left in coma from Covid is
OL,4,Creunited with doctors who saved his
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FFour years since the start of the
OL,8,Fpandemic, staff have described how
OL,9,Fcare on the wards had to be completely
OL,10,Ftransformed - and say we must not
OL,11,Fforget the unity and fortitude shown
OL,12,Fduring those unprecented times.
OL,14,FAnwar was on a ventilator for about 30
OL,15,Fdays before he was given a
OL,16,Ftracheostomy.
OL,18,F"It was a very, very tough time at
OL,19,Fthat time, but because when I woke up,
OL,20,FI'd slept through most of it, because
OL,21,FI was in a coma," Anwar said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
