OL,3,CMan who was left in coma from Covid is
OL,4,Creunited with doctors who saved his
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,F"But since I woke up, it's just been
OL,8,Fpositive how Subodh and all his team
OL,9,Flooked after me, the nurses, the
OL,10,Fdoctors.
OL,12,F"It was such good care - I couldn't
OL,13,Fask for more, and this is the reason
OL,14,Fwhy I'm standing here today."
OL,16,FAsked about how it feels to meet Anwar
OL,17,Fagain, Dr Subodh Tote, head of
OL,18,Fintensive care at Frimley Park
OL,19,FHospital said: "It's incredible."
