OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FSpeaking directly to Anwar, he added:
OL,8,F"It's a real uplifting thing for us,
OL,9,Freally, because we've had to deal with
OL,10,Fso much, and what you actually
OL,11,Frepresent to us is not just one
OL,12,Fpatient.
OL,14,F"You represent the hundreds and the
OL,15,Fthousands of patients all of us
OL,16,Ftreated during that time, and what a
OL,17,Fdifference it made.
OL,19,F"It makes it worthwhile what we did.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
