OL,5,Clife
OL,7,F"There's a lot that didn't make it,
OL,8,Fbut you remind us of everything that
OL,9,Fwe did and why we did it."
OL,11,F"I count my days every day," Anwar
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"I'm thankful every day for how much
OL,15,Fyou looked after me - that's why I'm
OL,16,Fstanding here today.
OL,18,F"When I woke up, I knew how close I
OL,19,Fcame to death.
