OL,3,CMan who was left in coma from Covid is
OL,4,Creunited with doctors who saved his
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,F"Being 30 days in a coma, I lost a lot
OL,8,Fof weight. I'll put it back on because
OL,9,FI love food, but I lost a lot of
OL,10,Fweight.
OL,12,F"It was like three stone almost in
OL,13,Fthat sort of two months I was here,
OL,14,Fand when I woke up, it was really,
OL,15,Freally tough.
OL,17,F"But no one left me, so I'm very, very
OL,18,Fthankful for that."
